lyrics:
29 contributorsdon’t wanna know lyricsverse 1
how are you feeling
do you like the show
are you tired of it
never mind i dont wanna know
are you finding it boring
too fast too slow

cause i dont wanna know

verse 2
do i have your attention
yes or no
i bet id guess the answer
but i dont wanna know
am i on in the background
are you on your phone
id ask you what youre watching
but i dont wanna know

verse 3
is there anyone out there
or am i all alone
it wouldnt make a difference
still i dont wanna know
i thought itd be over by now
but i got a while to go
id give away the ending
but you dont wanna kn—you might also like2embed
